title: Miss Australia 1959
brief_description: A segment from the 1959 Miss Australia Quest held in Brisbane’s Festival Hall during Queensland’s centenary celebrations. Miss Jean Stanbury of Western Australia is announced as the winner. Miss Australia 1958 is present as one of the judges.
